display_content.json_block:
{"language": "html", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Claude Headless Setup — 1단계 가이드</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600&family=Pretendard:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg: #0d0f14;
    --bg2: #13161e;
    --bg3: #1a1e2a;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    --border-active: rgba(139,92,246,0.5);
    --purple: #8b5cf6;
    --purple-dim: rgba(139,92,246,0.15);
    --teal: #2dd4bf;
    --teal-dim: rgba(45,212,191,0.12);
    --amber: #f59e0b;
    --amber-dim: rgba(245,158,11,0.12);
    --green: #22c55e;
    --green-dim: rgba(34,197,94,0.12);
    --red: #ef4444;
    --text: #e2e8f0;
    --text-muted: #64748b;
    --text-dim: #94a3b8;
    --mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    --sans: 'Pretendard', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    --radius: 10px;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.7;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 0;
  }

  /* ── Header ── */
  .header {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 28px 40px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .header-left h1 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .header-left p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .progress-bar-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .progress-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    min-width: 40px;
    text-align: right;
  }
  .progress-track {
    width: 160px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--purple), var(--teal));
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: width 0.4s ease;
    width: 0%;
  }

  /* ── Layout ── */
  .container {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 40px 80px;
  }

  /* ── Phase label ── */
  .phase-label {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--purple);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    background: var(--purple-dim);
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.25);
  }

  /* ── Steps ── */
  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-line {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-num {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .step.done .step-num {
    background: var(--green-dim);
    border-color: var(--green);
    color: var(--green);
  }
  .step.active .step-num {
    background: var(--purple-dim);
    border-color: var(--purple);
    color: var(--purple);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(139,92,246,0.1);
  }

  .step-connector {
    width: 1.5px;
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 20px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 4px 0;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .step.done .step-connector {
    background: rgba(34,197,94,0.3);
  }

  /* ── Step card ── */
  .step-card {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .step.active .step-card {
    border-color: var(--border-active);
    background: var(--bg3);
  }
  .step.done .step-card {
    border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.2);
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  .step-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .step.active .step-title { color: var(--purple); }
  .step.done .step-title { color: var(--text-muted); }

  .step-badge {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .badge-time { background: var(--teal-dim); color: var(--teal); }
  .badge-done { background: var(--green-dim); color: var(--green); }
  .badge-warn { background: var(--amber-dim); color: var(--amber); }

  .step-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── Step body (collapsible) ── */
  .step-body {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .step.active .step-body { display: flex; }

  /* ── Substep ── */
  .substep {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .substep-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .substep-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ── Code block ── */
  .code-block {
    position: relative;
    background: #080a0f;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .code-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .code-lang {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: var(--mono);
  }
  .code-copy {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .code-copy:hover { color: var(--teal); border-color: var(--teal); }
  .code-copy.copied { color: var(--green); border-color: var(--green); }
  .code-body {
    padding: 16px 18px;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  pre {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #a8b4d0;
    white-space: pre;
  }
  .c-comment { color: #3d5068; }
  .c-cmd { color: var(--teal); }
  .c-arg { color: #f4a261; }
  .c-str { color: #86efac; }
  .c-flag { color: var(--amber); }
  .c-out { color: #64748b; font-style: italic; }

  /* ── Callout ── */
  .callout {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .callout-info { background: var(--teal-dim); border: 1px solid rgba(45,212,191,0.2); color: var(--text-dim); }
  .callout-warn { background: var(--amber-dim); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2); color: #d4a853; }
  .callout-success { background: var(--green-dim); border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.2); color: #6ee7a0; }
  .callout-icon { font-size: 15px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

  /* ── Check item ── */
  .check-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .check-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .check-box {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--bg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .check-box.checked {
    background: var(--green-dim);
    border-color: var(--green);
  }
  .check-box.checked::after {
    content: '✓';
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ── Step complete button ── */
  .btn-complete {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: var(--purple-dim);
    border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--purple);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    align-self: flex-start;
    font-family: var(--sans);
  }
  .btn-complete:hover {
    background: rgba(139,92,246,0.25);
    border-color: var(--purple);
  }

  /* ── Final card ── */
  .final-card {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 32px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 32px;
    display: none;
  }
  .final-card.visible { display: block; }
  .final-emoji { font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .final-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .final-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 24px; }
  .test-command {
    background: #080a0f;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--teal);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: left;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ── Nav dots ── */
  .nav-dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .nav-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--border);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-dot.done { background: var(--green); }
  .nav-dot.active { background: var(--purple); width: 20px; border-radius: 3px; }

  /* ── Scrollbar ── */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border); border-radius: 3px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <div class="header-left">
    <h1>Claude Headless Setup</h1>
    <p>1단계 · MacBook as Remote Server</p>
  </div>
  <div class="progress-bar-wrap">
    <span class="progress-label" id="progress-label">0 / 5</span>
    <div class="progress-track">
      <div class="progress-fill" id="progress-fill"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <div class="phase-label">
    ⬡ Phase 1 — MacBook as Server + Tailscale + tmux
  </div>

  <div class="nav-dots" id="nav-dots"></div>

  <!-- ══ STEP 1 ══ -->
  <div class="step active" id="step-1" onclick="activateStep(1)">
    <div class="step-line">
      <div class="step-num" id="num-1">01</div>
      <div class="step-connector"></div>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-header">
          <div class="step-title">맥북 SSH 활성화</div>
          <span class="step-badge badge-time">2분</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step-desc">맥북을 원격에서 접속할 수 있도록 OpenSSH 서버를 켭니다.</div>
        <div class="step-body">

          <div class="substep">
            <div class="substep-title">① 시스템 설정에서 켜기</div>
            <div class="substep-desc">시스템 설정 → 일반 → 공유 → <strong style="color:var(--text)">원격 로그인</strong> 토글 ON. 활성화하면 SSH 사용자 목록이 나타납니다. "모든 사용자"로 설정하거나 본인 계정만 허용합니다.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="substep">
            <div class="substep-title">② 터미널에서 확인</div>
            <div class="code-block">
              <div class="code-header">
                <span class="code-lang">bash</span>
                <button class="code-copy" onclick="copyCode(this)">copy</button>
              </div>
              <div class="code-body"><pre><span class="c-comment"># SSH 서비스 상태 확인</span>
<span class="c-cmd">sudo</span> <span class="c-arg">systemsetup</span> <span class="c-flag">-getremotelogin</span>
<span class="c-out"># → Remote Login: On  이 나오면 정상</span>

<span class="c-comment"># 내 로컬 IP 확인 (나중에 필요)</span>
<span class="c-cmd">ipconfig</span> <span class="c-arg">getifaddr</span> <span class="c-flag">en0</span>
<span class="c-out"># → 192.168.x.x</span></pre></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="callout callout-warn">
            <span class="callout-icon">⚠</span>
            <span>같은 Wi-Fi 안에서는 로컬 IP로 접속됩니다. 카페·외부 네트워크에서 접속하려면 다음 단계 Tailscale이 필요합니다.</span>
          </div>

          <button class="btn-complete" onclick="completeStep(1, event)">✓ 완료 — 다음 단계로</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ STEP 2 ══ -->
  <div class="step" id="step-2" onclick="activateStep(2)">
    <div class="step-line">
      <div class="step-num" id="num-2">02</div>
      <div class="step-connector"></div>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-header">
          <div class="step-title">Tailscale 설치 — 어디서든 접속</div>
          <span class="step-badge badge-time">5분</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step-desc">공유기·포트포워딩 없이 맥북과 iPhone을 하나의 가상 네트워크로 연결합니다.</div>
        <div class="step-body">

          <div class="substep">
            <div class="substep-title">① 맥북에 설치</div>
            <div class="code-block">
              <div class="code-header">
                <span class="code-lang">bash</span>
                <button class="code-copy" onclick="copyCode(this)">copy</button>
              </div>
              <div class="code-body"><pre><span class="c-comment"># Homebrew로 설치</span>
<span class="c-cmd">brew</span> <span class="c-arg">install</span> <span class="c-flag">--cask</span> tailscale

<span class="c-comment"># 설치 후 실행 & 로그인</span>
<span class="c-cmd">open</span> <span class="c-arg">-a</span> Tailscale
<span class="c-comment"># → 상단 메뉴바 아이콘 클릭 → Log in → 브라우저 인증</span>

<span class="c-comment"># Tailscale IP 확인 (100.x.x.x 형태)</span>
<span class="c-cmd">tailscale</span> <span class="c-arg">ip</span> <span class="c-flag">-4</span>
<span class="c-out"># → 100.x.x.x  ← 이 IP가 iPhone에서 사용할 주소</span></pre></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="substep">
            <div class="substep-title">② iPhone에 설치</div>
            <div class="substep-desc">App Store → <strong style="color:var(--text)">Tailscale</strong> 검색 → 설치. <strong style="color:var(--text)">동일한 계정으로 로그인</strong>합니다. 로그인 후 맥북이 목록에 나타나면 연결 성공입니다.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="substep">
            <div class="substep-title">③ 연결 테스트</div>
            <div class="code-block">
              <div class="code-header">
                <span class="code-lang">bash — 맥북 터미널</span>
                <button class="code-copy" onclick="copyCode(this)">copy</button>
              </div>
              <div class="code-body"><pre><span class="c-comment"># Tailscale 상태 확인</span>
<span class="c-cmd">tailscale</span> <span class="c-arg">status</span>
<span class="c-out"># iPhone과 맥북이 둘 다 보이면 성공</span>

<span class="c-comment"># iPhone → 맥북 ping 테스트 (iPhone Termius에서)</span>
<span class="c-cmd">ping</span> <span class="c-arg">100.x.x.x</span>
<span class="c-out"># → 응답 있으면 완벽</span></pre></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="callout callout-info">
            <span class="callout-icon">ℹ</span>
            <span>Tailscale은 WireGuard 기반 VPN입니다. 100.x.x.x 주소는 어떤 네트워크에서든 맥북의 고정 주소처럼 동작합니다. 공인 IP가 바뀌어도 항상 같은 주소로 접속됩니다.</span>
          </div>

          <button class="btn-complete" onclick="completeStep(2, event)">✓ 완료 — 다음 단계로</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ STEP 3 ══ -->
  <div class="step" id="step-3" onclick="activateStep(3)">
    <div class="step-line">
      <div class="step-num" id="num-3">03</div>
      <div class="step-connector"></div>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-header">
          <div class="step-title">tmux 설정 — 세션 영속성</div>
          <span class="step-badge badge-time">5분</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step-desc">SSH 연결이 끊겨도 Claude Code가 계속 실행되도록 tmux로 세션을 유지합니다.</div>
        <div class="step-body">

          <div class="substep">
            <div class="substep-title">① 설치 & 기본 설정</div>
            <div class="code-block">
              <div class="code-header">
                <span class="code-lang">bash</span>
                <button class="code-copy" onclick="copyCode(this)">copy</button>
              </div>
              <div class="code-body"><pre><span class="c-comment"># tmux 설치</span>
<span class="c-cmd">brew</span> <span class="c-arg">install</span> tmux

<span class="c-comment"># ~/.tmux.conf 에 편의 설정 추가</span>
<span class="c-cmd">cat</span> <span class="c-flag">>></span> <span class="c-arg">~/.tmux.conf</span> <span class="c-flag"><<'EOF'</span>
<span class="c-str">set -g mouse on</span>
<span class="c-str">set -g history-limit 50000</span>
<span class="c-str">set -g base-index 1</span>
<span class="c-str">set -g status-style 'bg=#13161e fg=#64748b'</span>
<span class="c-str">set -g status-right '#[fg=#8b5cf6]%H:%M #[fg=#64748b]| #H'</span>
<span class="c-str">EOF</span>

<span class="c-comment"># 설정 적용</span>
<span class="c-cmd">tmux</span> <span class="c-arg">source</span> <span class="c-flag">~/.tmux.conf</span> <span class="c-arg">2>/dev/null</span> <span class="c-flag">||</span> <span class="c-cmd">true</span></pre></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="substep">
            <div class="substep-title">② Claude Agent 세션 생성</div>
            <div class="code-block">
              <div class="code-header">
                <span class="code-lang">bash</span>
                <button class="code-copy" onclick="copyCode(this)">copy</button>
              </div>
              <div class="code-body"><pre><span class="c-comment"># 'claude-agent' 라는 이름의 세션 생성</span>
